{"tid":2292602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個傻仔唔見咗銀包","createTime":"2020-11-19T15:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T15:18:25.000Z","uid":77015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"11d2cd82e407232546b512cae655512aff0b9d3a","tid":2292602,"uid":77015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T15:18:25.000Z","msg":"我就係嗰個傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期日係天水圍新北江地下間烘焙舖買嘢既時候仲係到<br />\n之後行咗後面間百佳買少少嘢<br />\n我係用apple pay比錢既<br />\n但我無印象有拎過銀包出嚟<br />\n之後就坐朋友車同去朋友屋企玩<br />\n來回番屋企都係朋友車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到星期二先發現唔見左<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Td63FeL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTd63FeL.png&h=693092df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n類似咁既樣<br />\n入面有幾百蚊，身分證，信用卡，提款卡<br />\n個銀包我自己整，好鐘意，希望搵番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望連登大神幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}